estern binary reason, these writers leave open the possibility of psychic liberation of African Americans in the West.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aAfrican American Studies : African American Studies. 4aCultural Studies : Cultural Studies. 4aLiterature : Literary Criticism. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / African-American.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781438448367?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438448367423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438448367/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles